column5: That I'd post a few of the great deals from the Angling Outfitters booth here @ the London Show  Nautilus Inflatable Life vest model NI700CTRY @ $99 Reg $189  OffShore Inline boards complete with OR18 release, red release and flag kit @ $49.99 each  Cheers G
The board and life vests were going as if they were being discontinued!  fyi, if you planning on heading down tomorrow for a lfe vest they're sold out.  Cheers G.
Nice seeing you again Gavin... To bad we did not get to spend time for a coffee as we were both busy... may be next time
